Weapons were being distributed to thousands of citizens in Iraq in anticipation of a  United States attack, and preparations were being made to evacuate Baghdad.
Western  visitors to Kuwait were rounded up and are safe in Baghdad.
Iraq said the invasion forces began to leave Kuwait Sunday.
President branded that as a  lie.
The United States aircraft carrier Independence is now on station in the Arabian Sea.
Japan and the European Community joined in the embargo of Iraqi oil.
The reduced  export of Iraqi oil caused the closure of one pipeline across Turkey, and reduced flow in  the other. 
